Senate, which is trying Mr Collor on corruption charges and will impeach him
if it finds him guilty. The trial started last week. Yesterday, the first
prosecution witnesses were called to testify before a packed Senate. They
include Mr Luis Motta Veiga, former head of Petrobras, the state oil
company.
