FT  03 NOV 92 / UK Company News: Embassy Property reduces deficit
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Embassy Property Group reported pre-tax losses for the year to March 31 of
Pounds 7.8m compared with Pounds 9.49m, after a fall from Pounds 6.64m to
Pounds 3.99m in exceptional items.
Turnover dipped from Pounds 15.5m to Pounds 13.4m and losses per share were
